</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:Sojourner_Truth_1864_npg_2002_90.jpg" class="image" title="Sojourner Truth 1864 npg 2002 90.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/65/Sojourner_Truth_1864_npg_2002_90.jpg/200px-Sojourner_Truth_1864_npg_2002_90.jpg" width="200" height="332" border="0" /></a><br />
<div style="padding-top:2pt;"><span style="">photograph by <a href="/wiki/Mathew_Brady" title="Mathew Brady">Mathew Brady</a>, an <a href="/wiki/Albumen_silver_print" title="Albumen silver print" class="mw-redirect">albumen silver print</a> from approximately 1864</span></div>
